   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ensuring Safety of Garments Workers in Bangladesh</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">No one can imagine the economic development of Bangladesh without considering the contribution of the garments sector. This sector has emerged as the single largest export sector in Bangladesh with 78.14 percent share in total national export in FY 2010-11 (iART 2011). It comprises of 16 percent GDP that has created scope for the employment opportunity of 10.72 percent labor force of which 6.83 percent are directly involved (Ahmed, 2013).</narrative>
  </description>
